Key Match Events: Four different Arizona relievers gave up a run or more
Marcus Semien, Corey Seager and Jonah Heim each homered on the night
The Rangers scored 10-0 in the fourth inning
Pre-Game Insights: The Diamondbacks came into the game with the intention of letting their bullpen handle the entire night
Similar strategy used in a 6-5 win over the Philadelphia Phillies in Game 4 of the NLCS
Post-Match Reflections: Arizona's offensive revival may have at least swung some back in their favor
The Rangers need just one more win in this series to secure the championship
The Diamondbacks are now just hoping to get this series back to Texas
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Rangers have been incredible on the road in October, winning 10 straight games away from home this postseason
Corey Seager won the 2023 World Series MVP award after Game 5 win vs. Diamondbacks
